name: Countless convergences – always a choice
description:
Multiple analog and digital pieces combined into a new arrangement; further digital work performed. 

In every moment it is all there. The existance blazes in countless fractals, potentialities beyond anything calculable. Forms and orders of things are not static – they morph with eye, I. What comes into being is also what is being seen...where does your eye lead you? Or what leads the eye? What will you choose to see and bring into being in the vast sea of countless possibilities? Isn't the choice of this existance also yours?
